title: Different outdoor professions carry different risks for skin cancer

title_detail.value: Different outdoor professions carry different risks for skin cancer

summary: One of the main risk factors for non-melanoma skin cancer (NMSC), the most common cancer worldwide, is solar ultraviolet radiation.
